@startuml
title Cart to Order Flow
actor Customer
participant Frontend
participant Backend
database DB

Customer -> Frontend: Browse foods
Frontend -> Backend: GET /api/foods
Backend -> DB: Query available foods
DB --> Backend: List<Food>
Backend --> Frontend: Render foods

Customer -> Frontend: Add to cart
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/carts/add
Backend -> DB: Add/Update Cart and CartItems

Customer -> Frontend: Place order
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/orders
Backend -> DB: Validate availability for each item
alt all available
  Backend -> DB: Create Order and OrderItems
  Backend -> Frontend: Return OrderId
else some unavailable
  Backend -> Frontend: 400 Bad Request
end
@enduml
